SOLICITATION NO: 25-FAC-8892
TITLE:           Integrated Custodial and Janitorial Services 
                 (Main Campus & Athletic Facilities)
ISSUING AGENCY:  North Summit University (NSU)
                 Office of Procurement & Strategic Sourcing
DATE ISSUED:     December 3, 2025

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0 INSTRUCTIONS TO PROPOSERS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.1 INTRODUCTION
North Summit University ("University") invites proposals from qualified vendors 
to provide comprehensive custodial services for 34 campus buildings, totaling 
approximately 1,650,000 gross square feet (GSF). The University seeks a 
performance-based contract where the vendor manages all labor, supervision, 
equipment, and cleaning supplies to maintain APPA Level 2 standards universally, 
with Level 1 standards in executive areas.

